revisions.rev:
[[Maccabi Haifa F.C.]] is an [[Israel]]i [[association football|football]] club based in [[Haifa]]. The club was founded in 1913 (as Maccabi "Hagibor" Haifa). Their first involvement in [[UEFA]] competition was in 1993, when they entered the Cup Winners' Cup.
